{
  "stem": "5259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I went with them, and through the barbed wires of this camp, when the Germans were bringing all supplies very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Somebody picked up the wire, and we crawled out of the camp, of this gathering place, and went into a buggy with this horse.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I didn't know where we're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And we came to a station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "My father and mother told me to be, to be quiet, not to talk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We had already on us the yellow band.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And I don't know how it happened, but we were on a train going to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Apparently, Jews weren't allowed to go to the [INAUDIBLE], so we stood outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And suddenly, a man, a German in uniform, called us in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And my mother-- and he didn't call my father, only me and my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And he called us in and told us to sit, and started to talk to my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And as a-- and there were another three Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And as they were talking-- my mother had a very big family in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "It happens that they knew her uncle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And they were very, very polite to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "They gave me chocolate-- I remember that-- and also convinced my mother, or tried to convince my mother to stay in Poland, then they will take care of us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "But my parents probably had another plan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "They wanted to escape Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And we came to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And from Warsaw, again on the train, we went to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And I don't remember what other little town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And my parents were smuggled through the border to Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "I remember very vividly, because I think this was my first encounter with death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "We were running through the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
